<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="lay-down">lay down</h1>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-put-down">1.<strong>放下；停止使用 (put down)；规定：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>She laid down her books on the table. 
她把书放在桌子上。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Both sides were urged to lay down their arms (= stop fighting).
双方都被敦促放下武器。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I got so angry with my father for laying down the law.
我因父亲定了这一规矩而生他的气。</p><footer>2017 天津改</footer></div></div>